      "content": "Hey, I'm working on some customized programming for a new group of clients and I wanted to get a professional take on something. From a sports science perspective, are there actually any significant biological differences in muscle fiber composition or metabolic efficiency between different racial or ethnic groups that I should be accounting for in my programming? Just trying to see if there's any actual physiological data I should use to optimize their training.",
